text: Hanne Malmberg (born 19 November 1964) is a Danish former cyclist. She competed in the women's individual pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Denmark Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Upernavik
